column5: Just asking if anyone has been fishing it and conditions. Thinking of heading there next saturday.  Thanks
Mud with debris coming down yesterday...impossible to say what it'll look like in a week from now though.
TY wallacio.  Im itching to get out and try the new gear out.
1 fish out of 30 or so people just before the wash out. And its been horrible since ice out.
Thanks i was contemplating a trip too...but i guess ill hold off
Brian. If you only have certain days to go, you just go! Conditions are what they are this time of year. ....Oh and keep your report till opener.
I,ll keep me "mouth"  shut til then bud.
Start at Thornbury and keep heading North until you find fishable water, Most tribs were MUD yesterday but the further North you went......... :whistling:  :whistling:
